                    <svg class="text-purple-600 absolute right-5 bottom-6 text-7xl" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" role="img" width="1em" height="1em" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
